 📊 Excel Sales Dashboard – Project_007

Welcome to my Excel-based Sales Dashboard! 🚀  
This project was built using advanced Excel features like **Pivot Tables**, **Macros**, and **VBA**.

---

📁 Project Files

Project_007.xlsm → Fully functional Excel dashboard.
dashboard_007.jpeg  → Screenshot preview of the dashboard.



## 📌 Features Covered

- Dynamic Pivot Table summaries
- Macro Automation
- VBA scripting logic
- Interactive Data Visualizations



## 📸 Preview

![Dashboard Preview](dashboard_007.jpeg)

---

## 💡 How to Use

1. Download `Project_007.xlsm`.
2. Open in Excel (enable macros).
3. Explore dashboard, pivot filters, and visual reports.



## 🧠 Practice Purpose

Anyone interested in:
- Excel automation
- Dashboard design
- Learning Pivot + Macros + VBA  
Can download and practice.

